<title>USA: MBIA Inc Q1 earnings summary.</title>
<headline>MBIA Inc Q1 earnings summary.</headline>
<dateline>ARMONK, N.Y. 1997-05-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			  $2.08		    $1.81</p>
<p> Net			 90,939		   77,625</p>
<p> Revs		     153,867		  130,197</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  43,700		   42,936</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTES: Operating earnings per share $1.99 for Q1 1997 vs $1.75 for Q1 1996. Core earnings, which exclude capital gains, premiums from refunded items and non-recurring items, were $1.81 per share for Q1 1997 vs $1.60 for Q1 1996.</p>
